Package: easyabc
Architecture: any
Depends: abcmidi, abcm2ps, ghostscript, ffmpeg, libfluidsynth3, fluid-soundfont-gm, python3-wxgtk4.0, python3-wxgtk-media4.0, python3-pygame,
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Suggests: fluidsynth, jackd
Description: An open source ABC editor for Windows, OSX and Linux.
  EasyABC allows the user to create, edit, view, play, convert music written in the ABC music notation language.
  It relies on external programs like abc2midi, abcm2ps, fluidsynth.